Class StdoutMsgListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.interpss.common.msg.StdoutMsgListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IpssMsgListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class StdoutMsgListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IpssMsgListener
    Output msg to the standard screen output, depending the output level. All msg with its msg level >= the defined output level will be out to the stdout.
